---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Interests - Ramy Ghorayeb"
  description="A Glimpse Into What I'm Curious About and Exploring Outside of Work."
>
  <div class="fade-in">
    <!-- Page Title -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16">Interests</h1>

    <!-- Interests Content -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <!-- Donations Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">Donations</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            We are paid fairly well in tech. I give back a small portion of my income to my favorite NGOs - organizations full of people dedicating their days to charitable work we often overlook. These are the ones I donate monthly to. I hope you can find one in this list that inspires you to start or increase your contribution.
          </p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
              <thead>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text);">Type</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text);">NGO</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-4 font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-text);">Description</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.doctorswithoutborders.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Doctors Without Borders</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Provides emergency medical aid in conflict zones and disaster areas worldwide, regardless of politics or religion.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.redcross.org.lb/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Lebanese Red Cross</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">The country has been living through a forever-crisis: the 2019 financial crisis, the 2020 port explosion then the Covid crisis, the 2022-2025 war. This is the most reliable and transparent organization in Lebanon to donate to.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.childrensrelieffund.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Children's Relief Fund</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Provides humanitarian aid and support to children in conflict zones and disaster areas around the world.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Humanitarian</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.restosducoeur.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Restos du Coeur</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Maybe the most scrutinized NGO in France. Provides a social safety net for those in need in the country.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Environment</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.rainforesttrust.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Rainforest Trust</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">They focus on land acquisition for high efficiency with low overhead.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Corruption</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.anticor.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Anticor</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Some of the most courageous people in France, fighting public corruption despite government pressure. They are responsible for the first-ever conviction of a former French President (Chirac case, 2011) for embezzling public funds.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.laquadrature.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Quadrature du Net</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Hardline defenders of privacy in the EU. They led in 2021 the GDPR charge that resulted in a €746 million fine —at the time, the largest in history—for non-consensual advertising targeting.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://www.wikipedia.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Wikipedia</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Free, crowdsourced encyclopedia maintaining the world's knowledge accessible to everyone.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Tech</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4"><a href="https://archive.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">Internet Archive</a></td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">A Library of Alexandria that's actually real. They are currently fighting for their legal life.</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Biohacking Protocol Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">Biohacking Protocol</h2>
          <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Countries I've Been To Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">Countries I've Been To + Next on the List</h2>
          <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Gym Log Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">Gym Log</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">Best Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">Current Training</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-text);">Table of Past Trainings</h3>
          <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- High School Writings Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">High School Writings</h2>
          <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            I used to write a lot when I was in high school. I still think some of them were pretty good. Trigger warning: one of them contains gore. (<a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1PtqCmPduUj8gmmW_rmlmOfFBih0bU9wX?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">link</a>)
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
